snippet.title: The Midpoint Formula
snippet.description:
Thanks to all of you who support me on Patreon. You da real mvps!   $1 per month helps!! :)  https://www.patreon.com/patrickjmt !! The Midpoint Formula - In this video I give the formula for finding the midpoint of two points and do one simple example to find the midpoint.
